data.description: Beautiful Custom built Ranch home located in Augusta Lake w/spectacular views of The Legends Golf Course.  The spacious home offers over 4,500 sqft of living space w/4 bedrooms, 3 and a half baths, full finished lower level, Central A/C, stamped concrete patio, and covered back deck with golf course views in Perry local school district.  This home has a nice open floor plan w/foyer that offers a home office & formal dining area that flows into the large living room w/gas fireplace and a kitchen that is perfect for entertaining.  The kitchen offers cherry cabinets, solid surface counters, stainless steel appliances, center island breakfast bar w/pull out shelving, dining area & pantry. Beautiful first floor Master Suite w/Glamour bath and walk-in closets that is located just off the kitchen and offers privacy from the other bedrooms.  The finished lower level provides more living space and offers another large living/media room along with a bar and full bath.  This home is perfect for those looking for one floor living w/ample space to entertain and enjoy.  This wont last long, schedule your showing today!
